  "summaries": [
    "The <b>Bug Net</b> is a <linked>tool</linked> used to capture certain <linked>critters</linked> as <linked>inventory</linked> items. It is swung like a <linked>broadsword</linked>, but it deals no damage. The Bug Net is nearly required in order to go <linked>fishing</linked>, as it is the initial and primary method of obtaining <linked>bait</linked>. Most critters that are insects, <linked>worms</linked>, or <linked>snails</linked> can function as bait once captured.",
