    "The <span class=\"i\"><linked>[img:Lavaproof Bug Net]</linked><span><span><linked>Lavaproof Bug Net</linked></span><span class=\"eico i1 i2 i4\" title=\"Desktop, Console and Mobile versions\"><b></b><i></i></span></span></span> and the <span class=\"i\"><linked>[img:Golden Bug Net]</linked><span><span><linked>Golden Bug Net</linked></span><span class=\"eico i1 i2 i4\" title=\"Desktop, Console and Mobile versions\"><b></b><i></i></span></span></span> are upgraded versions that are bigger, swing faster, and can destroy tall grass, vines, and uproot plants just like swords and other weapons do, despite dealing no damage."
